  "A US exporter sells $500,000 worth of goods to Europe. They expect payment of €460,000 in 3 months. They hedge with a forward contract at 1 EUR = 1.08 USD. If the spot rate at payment time drops to 1 EUR = 1.02 USD, how much did hedging save them?": "",
