  "$13,800": "",
  "$46,000": "",
  "$9,200": "",
  "With forward contract: €460,000 x 1.08 = $496,800. Without hedge (spot rate): €460,000 x 1.02 = $469,200. Hedging saved $496,800 - $469,200 = $27,600.": "",
  "A Big Mac costs $5.50 in the US and 650 yen in Japan. The actual exchange rate is 1 USD = 150 JPY. According to PPP, is the yen overvalued or undervalued?": "",
